news_header: An exciting election day in the U.S. with high voter turnout and notable events.
news_text: The election day in the United States was marked by vigorous voting and notable occurrences. The outcome of the presidential election remains uncertain, with candidates Kamala Harris and Donald Trump vying for the presidency. In Florida, a Republican supporter carried a puppet resembling Trump, while in Georgia, voter turnout is expected to be record high. A dog named Penny joined its owner to vote in Pennsylvania. Coverage of the elections is being provided by Yle’s journalists and photographers, with live updates available online and on various media platforms.
